{"tid":1538870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今個星期前線手足可唔可以忍一忍","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:39:22.000Z","uid":69291,"like":29,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"114903dbda0e55403305ae0742e0416511a3592d","tid":1538870,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:06:31.000Z","msg":"和理非&gt;死線&gt;升級<br />\n呢個係我地一貫既做法<br />\n依家佢吹大風會撤回, <br />\n同咩真相調查委員會(我覺得係啲垃圾委員會嚟)<br />\n如果今個星期我地都係衝<br />\n結果只會係畀彈藥對方<br />\n如果去到之後佢都係無回應其他四個<br />\n我地先再升級<br />\n做到收放自如<br />\n真正如水<br />\n<br />\n但集會遊行唔可以停<br />\n今個星期一定要出話畀佢知我地<br />\n五個要求一個都不能少<br />\n同埋最重要係我地支持美國訂立<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人權民主法案</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSKAOwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSKAOwu.jpg&h=c34631af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54263e04c3f39bd5e6b1f4ae4cbf05b73abd2d0","tid":1538870,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ea6e00fb9e44a477df1fff90cf91e2fd23f601","tid":1538870,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e96cd6808c7a06d7975976061f60898160f193","tid":1538870,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"