:46.000Z","msg":"短期內勇武轉做和理非先，原因有以下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 勇武要休養生息。<br />\n2. 凖勇武要練兵。<br />\n3. 集中資源去幫助受傷，被捕義士。<br />\n4. 和理非用和平手段去追求其他訴求。<br />\n5. 打好選戰。"},{"pid":"2828338f741b120d7ee61db0a47e1f40aa0beee6","tid":1538870,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"衝有衝既好<br />\n就係顯示出抗爭者唔會退讓既決心<br />\n但好大機會會畀對家同嚟大做文章<br />\n亦削弱衝既當性"},{"pid":"cb5e37c99eb162b23ca682531016013ad538e960","tid":1538870,"uid":244958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"只玩機場已經好和理非"},{"pid":"3726c0cc1e4da53e8d52d0b1e33ce1aa83e49516","tid":1538870,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"急！！要求增加置頂推文、中英對照版本功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538902</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9d6d51c9cd4775ec7b6613228cafe431bb7180f","tid":1538870,"uid":264382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:08.000Z","msg":"同意！"},{"pid":"11cb53f0546759647baf5cf0ddbaedc96273f8b3","tid":1538870,"uid":118827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"連續幾個禮拜都叫前線停<br />\n我諗都冇乜人會再聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01403442dce09790d55e238e1c817ff16425ed6e","tid":1538870,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"到底邊個先適合<br />\n我想一齊思考一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係我既原意"}]}